reviewText: Extremely informative.  Outstanding music composition and lyrics.  Pleasing to the mind and easy on the ears.
So cute, my two year old grandson loves this
some of the script could have been more interesting and better written
My kids loved watching it. Nice that you can just watch it through amazon prime.

I bought this video for my 2 year old son.  He seldom watches any tv and I found this type of video at the store, came home and looked on internet and found this at a great price, and great condition for being used.  Keeps him still for a few moments.

Thank you

My husband bought this movie for our son in Dec 2004. He watches this movie all of the time. He is 2 1/2 years old and can tell you all of the different kids of John Deere equipment.

He loves the popper the best. Great movie can not wait until part 2 comes out.
